<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Aula Gratuita: O Poder da Mentoria</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --rose: #C4596A;
    --rose-dark: #8B3343;
    --rose-light: #F7E8EB;
    --rose-pale: #FDF5F6;
    --gold: #C9923A;
    --gold-light: #F5E6D0;
    --cream: #FAF7F4;
    --charcoal: #2C2420;
    --warm-gray: #6B5F58;
    --border: #E8DDD8;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 70% 40%, rgba(196,89,106,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 20% 80%, rgba(201,146,58,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 60px 80px 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(196,89,106,0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,89,106,0.4);
    color: #F2A0AE;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .pill::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #F2A0AE;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.7); }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 4vw, 58px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rose);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 440px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .date-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .date-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--rose);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .date-icon .month {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1px;
  }

  .date-icon .day {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .date-info p {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .date-info span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .cta-hero {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--rose);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .cta-hero:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .cta-hero svg { transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .cta-hero:hover svg { transform: translateX(4px); }

  /* ── HERO RIGHT (form) ── */
  .hero-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 80px 60px 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .form-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 44px 40px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  }

  .form-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .form-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--cream);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    outline: none;
    appearance: none;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus {
    border-color: var(--rose);
    background: #fff;
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder { color: #B5A9A4; }

  .btn-submit {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--rose);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 15px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 8px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-submit:active { transform: scale(0.99); }

  .form-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #B5A9A4;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  .form-note svg { vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; }

  .social-proof {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .avatars {
    display: flex;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    margin-left: -6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--rose-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .avatar:first-child { margin-left: 0; }

  .social-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .social-text strong { color: var(--charcoal); }

  /* ── ABOUT SECTION ── */
  .section {
    padding: 100px 80px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 3vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose); }

  .section-body {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  /* ── WHAT YOU'LL LEARN ── */
  .topics-section {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 100px 80px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .topics-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: end;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .topics-header .section-title { color: #fff; }
  .topics-header .section-body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .topic-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .topic-card:first-child { border-radius: 16px 0 0 16px; }
  .topic-card:last-child { border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0; }

  .topic-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0;
    height: 2px;
    width: 0;
    background: var(--rose);
    transition: width 0.35s;
  }

  .topic-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
  .topic-card:hover::after { width: 100%; }

  .topic-num {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--rose);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .topic-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .topic-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── FOR WHO ── */
  .forwho-section {
    padding: 100px 80px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--rose-pale);
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .check-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .check-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .check-icon {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--rose);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .check-icon svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; }

  .visual-block {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 48px 40px;
    color: #fff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .visual-block::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px; right: 24px;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 160px;
    color: rgba(196,89,106,0.15);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .quote-author {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .quote-author strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }

  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .stat-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--rose);
    display: block;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    margin-top: 4px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* ── BOTTOM CTA ── */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 100px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .cta-section .section-title { text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 12px; }
  .cta-section .section-body { text-align: center; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }

  .cta-big {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--rose);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 18px 44px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(196,89,106,0.35);
  }

  .cta-big:hover { background: var(--rose-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(196,89,106,0.45); }

  .event-info-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .event-info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
  }

  .event-info-item svg { color: var(--rose); }

  /* ── PHOTO SECTION ── */
  .photo-section {
    padding: 100px 80px;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .photo-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .photo-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }

  .photo-img-wrap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 16px -16px -16px 16px;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    border-radius: 20px;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 520px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .photo-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .photo-section { padding: 64px 32px; }
    .profile-photo { height: 380px; }
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    padding: 32px 80px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  footer p { font-size: 13px; color: #B5A9A4; }

  /* ── SUCCESS STATE ── */
  .success-msg {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .success-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: #EDFAF5;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }

  .success-msg h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .success-msg p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--warm-gray); margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-left { padding: 60px 32px 40px; }
    .hero-right { padding: 0 32px 60px; }
    .form-card { max-width: 100%; }
    .section, .topics-section, .cta-section { padding: 64px 32px; }
    .topics-header, .forwho-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .topics-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .topic-card:first-child { border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0; }
    .topic-card:last-child { border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px; }
    .event-info-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="pill">Aula ao Vivo &amp; Gratuita</div>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Aula Gratuita · 27 de Maio</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">O Poder de<br><em>Ser Mentora</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Descubra o que é mentoria e como transformar experiência em impacto</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">Uma aula transformadora para quem quer entender o universo da mentoria, aprender como guiar outras pessoas e descobrir o impacto real que você pode gerar com a sua experiência.</p>

    <div class="date-badge">
      <div class="date-icon">
        <span class="month">Mai</span>
        <span class="day">27</span>
      </div>
      <div class="date-info">
        <p>Terça-feira, 27 de Maio de 2025</p>
        <span>20h30 · Online · Ao vivo</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="#inscricao" class="cta-hero">
      Garantir minha vaga gratuita
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right" id="inscricao">
    <div class="form-card">
      <h3>Reserve sua vaga</h3>
      <p>É gratuito. Preencha abaixo e receba o link de acesso no seu e-mail.</p>

      <div id="form-area">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Seu nome completo</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Como posso te chamar?">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Seu melhor e-mail</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="seuemail@exemplo.com">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="whatsapp">WhatsApp (com DDD)</label>
          <input type="tel" id="whatsapp" placeholder="(11) 99999-9999">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="area">Qual é a sua área de atuação?</label>
          <select id="area">
            <option value="" disabled selected>Selecione uma opção</option>
            <option>Saúde &amp; Bem-estar</option>
            <option>Negócios &amp; Empreendedorismo</option>
            <option>Educação &amp; Treinamento</option>
            <option>Tecnologia</option>
            <option>Marketing &amp; Comunicação</option>
            <option>RH &amp; Gestão de Pessoas</option>
            <option>Finanças &amp; Carreira</option>
            <option>Coaching &amp; Desenvolvimento Pessoal</option>
            <option>Outra área</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <button class="btn-submit" onclick="handleSubmit()">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          Quero participar da aula gratuita
        </button>

        <p class="form-note">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
          Seus dados estão seguros. Sem spam.
        </p>

        <div class="social-proof">
          <div class="avatars">
            <div class="avatar">A</div>
            <div class="avatar">M</div>
            <div class="avatar">C</div>
            <div class="avatar">R</div>
          </div>
          <div class="social-text">
            <strong>+240 pessoas</strong> já garantiram sua vaga
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="success-msg" id="success-msg">
        <div class="success-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1E9E6A" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Vaga garantida! 🎉</h4>
        <p>Fique de olho no seu e-mail. Você receberá o link de acesso em breve. Até dia 27!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="section">
  <p class="section-label">Sobre a aula</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">O que é mentoria<br>e <em>por que ela transforma vidas</em></h2>
  <p class="section-body">Mentoria não é coaching, não é consultoria e não é terapia. É algo único: a transmissão consciente de experiência, perspectiva e direção. Nessa aula, vamos explorar esse universo em profundidade — e você vai entender o que significa ser mentora e como essa prática pode transformar a carreira de quem você guia.</p>
</section>

<!-- TOPICS -->
<section class="topics-section">
